<paragraph blockId="108.[151,1430,581,603]" box="[151,1430,581,603]" pageId="108" pageNumber="109">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[151,288,581,603]" pageId="108" pageNumber="109">FIGURE 57.</emphasis>
Dorsal view of the male terminalia of 
<taxonomicName authority="Ferrari, 2017" authorityName="Ferrari" authorityYear="2017" box="[679,806,581,603]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="108" pageNumber="109" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="simulatus" status="n. sp.">
